The '''[[Incom Corporation/Legends|Incom]] GBk-785 hyperdrive''' was the [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrive]] unit commonly installed in the [[RZ-1 A-wing interceptor/Legends|RZ-1 A-wing interceptor]]. The class 1.0 GBk-785 was used to accelerate the A-wing to [[Hyperspace/Legends|supralight velocities]]. It was part of Incom's [[GBk series|GBk]] hyperdrive product line.

